Game Design Document

https://savetheworldgame.notion.site/Game-Design-Document-96e93acd57154301b08344fb2cd9db16?pvs=4 


Save the World: A systems game is a participatory sociotechnical systems design simulation research tool for modeling 
rapid failure complex societal challenge systemic solutions. Playing by natural universe rules, players are introduced to 
the urgency of current real-world issues around world how they are interconnected to those problems and the system patterns 
that created those problems such as, unsustainability, inequality and human suffering and demise. 
